headline.main: In Day of Pro-Trump Rallies, California March Turns Violent
headline.print_headline: In Day of Pro-Trump Rallies, California March Turns Violent

lead_paragraph: Supporters of Donald Trump clashed with counter-protesters at a rally in the famously left-leaning city of Berkeley, California, on a day of mostly peaceful gatherings in support of the U.S. president across the country.
